OL,3,CIn pictures: Troutbeck Hot Air Balloon
OL,4,CFestival
OL,6,FTroutbeck Hot Air Balloon Festival was
OL,7,Fa private event on Sunday 31st May
OL,8,F2026 for balloonists and their support
OL,9,Fcrews, raising money for four mental
OL,10,Fhealth charities:
OL,12,FFrom public areas and viewpoints,
OL,13,Faround 60 hot air balloons could be
OL,14,Fseen in the skies near Blencathra.
OL,15,FHere are some of those views in
OL,16,Fpictures.
