OL,3,CIn pictures: Troutbeck Hot Air Balloon
OL,4,CFestival
OL,6,FMentell is a Greater Manchester-based
OL,7,Fcharity with the mission to give men
OL,8,Faged 18+ the opportunity to talk in a
OL,9,Fsafe, confidential space, free from
OL,10,Fadvice and judgement, so they do not
OL,11,Fhave to keep their problems bottled up.
OL,13,FOne of those involved with the
OL,14,FFestival lost his brother to suicide.
OL,15,FOrganisers say, "It's a loss that
OL,16,Fnever leaves you." He also had a close
OL,17,Ffriend who tragically lost his young
OL,18,Fson in the same way.
