OL,3,CIn pictures: Troutbeck Hot Air Balloon
OL,4,CFestival
OL,6,FThe Farming Community Network seeks to
OL,7,F"walk with" farmers, farm workers and
OL,8,Ftheir families during times of
OL,9,Fdifficulty, uncertainty and change,
OL,10,Fsupporting around 10,000 people every
OL,11,Fyear, helping them navigate issues
OL,12,Fsuch as financial pressures, animal
OL,13,Fdisease outbreaks, mental health
OL,14,Fstruggles and family disputes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]
