OL,3,CIn pictures: Troutbeck Hot Air Balloon
OL,4,CFestival
OL,6,FOrganisers say "Without the goodwill
OL,7,Fand cooperation of farmers and
OL,8,Flandowners, ballooning simply would
OL,9,Fnot be possible. Pilots rely on their
OL,10,Funderstanding and support when landing
OL,11,Fin fields across the countryside, and
OL,12,Fthe ballooning community is incredibly
OL,13,Fgrateful for the relationship that has
OL,14,Fdeveloped over many years."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
